# samples.csv — intentionally empty until FASTQs exist

Do NOT add placeholder sample names that point at missing files.
Snakemake will fail with MissingInputException.

When reads are on Nepenthes, add one row per sample:

    sample_id,r1,r2
    my_sample,/scratch/odrew060/fastq/my_sample_R1.fq.gz,/scratch/odrew060/fastq/my_sample_R2.fq.gz

Paths can be absolute or relative to fastq_dir in config/config.yaml.
